comments.text: Here's an observation: Among the items on display contained in the backpack were both girls' bras. This suggests that at some time late on April 1st, both girls felt the need to liberate themselves. On basically all photos showing Lisanne, a bra strap is partially visible. Based on previous photos, the girls would wear a bra whenever they were in a public setting; this included moving along the trail for all we know. After image #508 (and #509?), they must have considered themselves out of public view and not expected to snap additional photos. Clearly, they would be off the trail, but where and why? Did the girls veer off the beaten path just after #508 to maybe take a dip, or did they head back? If they were confronted and forced off the path, how did their bras end up in the backpack? This detail continues to bother me.
comments.author: @tomsrensen9382
